// bisect: Sample in a per-slot HOF clone woke the wrong root.
// Sample had no clone_rebind override; the default recompile passed
// spec().id as top_id, so the clone's set_var wake targeted a root
// nobody drives — the slot never advanced. FIXED 2026-07-04:
// structural clone_rebind registering under the original top_id.
array::map([i64:1], |v| array::group(array::iter([i64:1, i64:2]) ~ "T", |n, _| n == i64:2))
